Detailed Description

template<class T>
class Util::StackList< T >

Thread linked list (thread unsafe)

The StackList descriptor is linked to the top element. We can define a stack list of Linkable cells: 

    StackList<X> Stk_of_X;

In insertion, cell must always be defined (not 0).

Warning:
In deletion, stack is not cleared
See also:
List, Queue
